text: Introducing AWS Card Clash Multiplayer Mode.

Face off against your friends
and put your AWS skills to the test,
in a head to head battle.

Simply generate a code to share with
your friends and you're ready to begin.

Play AWS Service Cards to complete the
architecture and outscore your opponent.

Use power ups to protect your board
and disrupt their plans,

and when Miss Gorilla crashes the party,
you'll both scramble to recover.

Play anywhere on PC, Mac,
or mobile devices.

Send the code
and get ready to learn AWS together.

AWS Card Clash multiplayer mode is available
now for free on AWS Skill Builder.
